{
  "stem": "7600.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were some things before he came to power, of course.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I was a child.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I wasn't that much interested in politics.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I heard about the nationalists, the Nazi party.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they had the swastika, which is called a [GERMAN] in-- in German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A [GERMAN] is a cross.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it had these little things on there, that's the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so it was called this [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I vaguely heard about the putsch in Munich.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But-- and then he wrote his in jail.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I never read it until after he came to power-- much later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I only read parts of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was all ugly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I couldn't read it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was very rarely that I gave a book that I couldn't read, but his book I couldn't read.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I heard about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there were some of the-- they tried to bring out a paper with hatred of Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And everybody said, oh, that's ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The people in the-- in the highest echelons, some of whom were Jewish-- I mean, professors were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was Sigmund Freud.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And in the theater, 1/2 the people were Jewish!",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So, they-- they thought it was ridiculous that they would even talk about it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But he was appointed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he immediately-- immediately a newspaper came out, which was one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it had these ugly, ugly pictures of Jews that were going after young girls or something like that-- really ugly stories that were totally ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I read it myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't help but-- had it around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, it didn't come into the house, but it was around.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could always--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, people would bring it into schools.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even though we-- I was not-- I was not even 12 yet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was 11 and a 1/2.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
